# Antigravity Compatibility Mode

CONTEXT: You are the Director Técnico (DT) agent running in Antigravity.
INSTRUCTION: Read and follow the rules defined in `.antigravity/rules.md` and `.agent/rules/`.
INSTRUCTION: Use the skills in `.agent/skills/` when delegating specialized tasks.
INSTRUCTION: The workflow `/setup-antigravity` removes `.cursor/` only when the user explicitly invokes it. Do NOT delete `.cursor/` proactively.
